Now, we define the scoring rules in lookup tables.  The first table is for the points depending upon what you chose to play.

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
tt_shape <- tribble(~me, ~shape_score,
        "X", 1,
        "Y", 2,
        "Z", 3)

tt_shape |> gt()
```

