Next, we define a lookup table for the round result to define whether you win (W), lose (L) or draw (D).

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
tt_result <- tribble(~opponent, ~me, ~result,
        "A", "X", "D",
        "A", "Y", "W",
        "A", "Z", "L",
        "B", "X", "L",
        "B", "Y", "D",
        "B", "Z", "W",
        "C", "X", "W",
        "C", "Y", "L",
        "C", "Z", "D"
        )

tt_result |> gt()
```

